{"tid":2139654,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如何同人講想爆石而不失雅氣？","createTime":"2020-08-04T12:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T13:07:10.000Z","uid":191338,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e75021c0871d6fb4cdaf9956a27bc76bc83f39fb","tid":2139654,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:14:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/j7RNIrvuakc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fj7RNIrvuakc&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Ydy%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=931d7a26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/j7RNIrvuakc</a><br />\n<br />\n英文文雅地有ans the call of nature呢種講法<br />\n<br />\n大小便又有冧把溫吐<br />\n<br />\nhow about cantonese?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上世紀地盤佬就有紥馬一詞<br />\n因為當時抽水馬桶坐廁仲未普及<br />\n大多數人都仲用緊踎廁<br />\n<br />\n直譯回應自然嘅呼喚又好awkward <br />\n仲可以用咩說法去表達想去痾屎，同時又能夠凸顯出香港人熱愛自由民主嘅公民質素？"},{"pid":"2f90e3b8ee2aebaec1058976dade5210a920c561","tid":2139654,"uid":55493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:15:39.000Z","msg":"婉轉 出恭"},{"pid":"e1109b1e4e766eda3afe5e89277c14da45509ed4","tid":2139654,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:16:36.000Z","msg":"咪爆石"},{"pid":"b2152b1149423c8108555b92958597615a7208f1","tid":2139654,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"我去廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a135a81ac1f5a9684802284e570cd396311fa0d0","tid":2139654,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:17:56.000Z","msg":"我而家要去廁所送黑警一程<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbf134589d1d5062c9117416658145bfc2dc5ba","tid":2139654,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:18:15.000Z","msg":"多數我都話「整理少少事先」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"